[02:48.331]I will shiver
[02:49.543]Shiver!
[02:50.509]Into the fire!
[02:51.663]You just get out alive!
[02:55.276]We'll let our worlds collide
[02:57.468]We are bigger!
[02:59.440]Make a promise that
[03:00.805]I cannot regret
[03:02.799]As long as I can see
[03:04.198]you but in secret
[03:05.910]I'll never
[03:06.897]I'll never
